fieldLabel.name: Population
fieldLabel.definition: This entry gives an estimate from the US Bureau of the Census based on statistics from population censuses, vital statistics registration systems, or sample surveys pertaining to the recent past and based on assumptions about future trends. This annual estimate does not reflect sudden population shifts due to conflicts, natural disasters, or other unexpected events.
